Ever since I started my running journey I realized I needed to make some changes to my daily routine….my diet to be specific.
I’ve been focusing on doing a better job with the way I fuel my body which means eating cleaner and healthier. With that said I’m super excited to announce my partnership with @applegate @chefreneeblackman put me on game and has been incorporating Applegate products into my meals every week, which has been key to helping me to Feel good, Look Good, and Do Better💯🔑🙌🏾

The first thing I told myself when I purchased my crib was that I MUST HAVE my own home gym🔑…..My man @chrishowell16 made that vision come to life and took it up another level with the custom AT accessories!! I can confidently say my mental and physical health have improved since we finished this project a couple months ago🙏🏾 This ain’t an ad……Its a pure thank you to my bro for helping me DO BETTER‼️👑🙏🏾

Attention Athletes:

WE HAVE LIVE ACTION TOMORROW GOING DOWN AT 12pm ET‼️ Join us as our team captains @jesssims @pelotonjenn lead #TeamActivate and #TeamValidate to their first and ONLY competition on the bike. The team that wins tomorrow will have the advantage before we compete on tread next week🔑 Remember, your individual output will determine your teams overall success….WE practiced at GAME SPEED for a reason. See you tomorrow 12PM sharp‼️ @onepeloton
